<p>I have been using <strong>ArtRage</strong>, <strong>Krita</strong> and <strong>Infinite Painter</strong> for many years now but I thought I would try that other well known digital art tool&hellip; <strong>emacs</strong>!</p>
<p>Using the built-in artist-mode now I really can truly live in emacs full time!</p>
